title: 2022 CFB Pick Em Week 6
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico are back for Week 6 of the CFB season. Dave is on top of the Path Hill and Bob Diaco standings still. However, this week's not about picks, it's about blogs. The whole squad is devoted to helping Rico crack the Top 20 Bloggers next week.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
